dde-desktop-videowallpaper-plugin (1.3) stable; urgency=medium

  * fix: HiDPI render correction using physical pixels for mpv FBO
    (contributed by @DonkeyKongG3me on Telegram)
  * fix: config cache not updating after external DConfig change
  * fix: enable/disable handler guard was always blocking turnOn/turnOff
  * fix: ffprobe no longer blocks the UI thread when selecting a video
  * fix: play() and refreshSource() no longer race to double-load video
  * fix: turnOn() leaked watcher and timer on double-call
  * fix: getVideos() now filters by video extension only
  * fix: use qobject_cast instead of dynamic_cast in event filter

 -- K4RLT <karl@karl-pc>  Mon, 09 Mar 2026 08:57:41 +0000

dde-desktop-videowallpaper-plugin (1.2) stable; urgency=medium

  * be compatible with deepin 25
  * remove Qt5 support, focusing solely on Qt6
  * fix org.deepin.dde-shell root widget has titlebar
  * use libmpv instead of QtMultimedia
  * fix dde-shell random crash issue
  * be compatible with dde-file-manager 6.5.7

 -- K4RLT <karl@karl-pc>  Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:05:00 +0800

